		<title>假日銷售強勁，阿迪達斯股價走高</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/adidas-shares-higher-strong-holiday-sales</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 18:36:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市場新聞及觀點]]></category>
